Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓真好强啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人组队的话 这点怪物小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的装备也分给你们吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有好多呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「因为我们是伙伴啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真是太逗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算啦 反正还免费送装备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这装备也太强了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人刷怪也轻轻松松！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不带拓真也无所谓了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓！无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是做梦啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太 太近了吧 你们俩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然真是艳福不浅啊…
