Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1068,545)}第7话\N人心变幻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跟希比和赛勒丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知会昨天奇拉王子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去向领主加尔弗德大人报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上多小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多小心的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险者们也许还会袭击你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇拉王子也还会来听你的答复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁来 我都不会把雪拉交出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要果断拒绝哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就都结束啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会发生战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿下报酬 任务就圆满完成啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次虽然避免了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是觉得 要时刻做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算重现 我那个世界的药水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害！药水吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王非一日可成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为强者 更不能疏于这些基本的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这要怎么做啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和「十字幻想曲」的贴图又不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要混合起来就行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会吵你的！能让我看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我会压力山大！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一丁点就能窥见精灵的至宝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起药水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想要润滑液啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波 涛 胸 涌！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就能做好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然做好了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过专业人士制作药水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没你这么快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在乳摇了三下的时间里做出了药水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 下意识地动手操作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然自己是毫无知识的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要将注意力转移到别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能变成游戏里的顶级熟练调和师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间做好药水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不做了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还要做…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好看着吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有必要学习做药水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细盯着我的手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！我看着呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也看着呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Q弹嫩滑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头头！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就能看见头头了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 熟练调和师！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为魔王 这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次看到这么操作的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么什么都会 迪亚布罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你平时都摆出一副恐怖的表情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死！大意了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢迪亚布罗刚才的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对！就是这表情！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在来这个世界之前 我从没这样被人开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能不用扮演魔王 普普通通地说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望 这样的时光…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能一直继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在害羞什么啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞的魔王就不是魔王了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗还会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 迪亚布罗…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 迪亚布罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事 要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回古林伍德王国了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等、等…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古林伍德是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不应该在这浪费时间 要回去为王族尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾 蕾姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用跟她告别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起告别 我要快点回到哥哥身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 雪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 你一定会回我身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了我们都要尊重雪拉的决定吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么没精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉回古林伍德了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉不是会撒谎的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天她明明说过不会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我哪里惹到她了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望 这样的时光 能一直继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要颓废到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去救她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个白痴精灵 是不懂演戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要是懂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能领会更多东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子缺根筋 记性差得很
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也不会撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:10:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她昨天晚上 还和我谈到了将来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然听起来不太现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很有她的风格 是个可爱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她的梦想中 有我 也有迪亚布罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得这样的她 会离开我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有可能被施下了操纵意识的魔法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情 我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇拉来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又吹起了笛子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后 雪拉就不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的笛子 也许有什么魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「十字幻想曲」中没有这样的笛子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是 我没有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 还是和从前一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我单方面以为大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作多情的误会别人对我也有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得这一切都是被抛弃者的可悲妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…相信雪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是被施下魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也一定是昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去把雪拉带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再被拒绝 不想再受伤了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想被他人左右自己的感情！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆应该也是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我是雪拉的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我现在是迪亚布罗和蕾姆的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗？你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！就只有蕾姆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是你的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 迪亚布罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望这样的时光 能一直继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 蕾姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单枪匹马闯进精灵的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能保证全身而退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再见到雪拉一面 我就绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个有趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了见见那个擅自离开的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要面对如此高难度的挑战？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆·嘉蕾邬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤我的其中一人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你渴求魔王的力量吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王迪亚布罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了完成你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让你见识下 我这强大力量的片鳞半爪！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一同前去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉小姐的事 我也无法释然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做 也许会让你失去国家骑士的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想守护的 不是自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要帮助的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能丢下蕾姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明说过 你不需要派上什么用场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 看来还挺喜欢自找麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要从愚蠢王子手中 夺回雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做无谓的挣扎了 雪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这笛子是我们一族的秘宝吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就以只有精灵能听见的声音 把魔法施加在笛声中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经无法违抗这笛子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够随意改写 你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那表情真是杰作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果却惨遭背叛的混魔族！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 雪拉 我要改写了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会乖乖回答我的问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗要求你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你下了什么命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用隶从项圈对你下了不少命令吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让你做了什么样的侍奉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你做更厉害的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只命令过我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和蕾姆握手 保持笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能只是这样吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的没有再被命令过了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你也逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你的身体牢牢记住…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是属于谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的声音是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 我正要开始享受…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是史莱姆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被融化吃掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉食系的话是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这种只吃纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要融化我的衣服做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是为了准备传宗接代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像被大大的舌头舔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢膝盖内侧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个骚货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只觉得好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区雪拉还挺努力的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌哥哥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别惹毛我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然在传宗接代前我就会把你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被你凌辱 我还不如去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你还能嘴硬到几时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个聒噪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 我就帮你改写
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你想将一切奉献给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 迪亚布罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了 雪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入公务中的王子阵中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公务 这叫公务吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此无耻下流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是王族 也无法饶恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是助兴节目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论男女 都得有点情调吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我就该不惜将城市化作火海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要把雪拉留下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的…你真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这扯什么友情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没发现入侵者？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫们都是干什么吃的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没听见外头的声音吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么情况？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫们都去哪了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道自己干了些什么吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是国际问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引发战争也无所谓吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来确定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉是不是真的想回国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用恶毒的手段操纵了雪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么证据？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要再问问雪拉的心意就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉！说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该做什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回到古林伍德去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古林伍德是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不应该在这浪费时间 要回去为王族尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你清醒点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她都这么说了 你满足了吧 混魔族？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以隶从项圈主人之名命令你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受任何魔法拘束 将你内心真正的想法说出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉大人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改写！改写！改写！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉大人！不要输啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出你的真心话 雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是属于我的 雪拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的真实心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要自由！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和迪亚布罗 和蕾姆 永永远远在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 伙伴才是最重要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该受到制裁 奇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废物 废物 废物！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个个都让我这么火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直一点意思都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区愚民 嚣张什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！不可以用那只召唤兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要判你们全体死刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵族的秘宝 能破坏这个世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让我开心的这个世界 干脆毁灭掉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有胆量挑战我 你就准备好面对相应的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧 召唤九头蛇！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊 迪亚布罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是绝对赢不了那召唤兽的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是精灵的镇国之宝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了 等着后悔吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧 混魔族！
