Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:09.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{blur3\fad(100,100)}心烦意乱　隐隐作痛　这一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{blur3\fad(100,100)}这一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:29.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}在你身旁　就苦闷不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:33.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}不住发出叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:40.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}能不能告诉我　你喜欢去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:43.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}顺便请问　你喜欢什么类型呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:50.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}任谁也无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:57.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}无可奈何　这就是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:02.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}早上醒来　就想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:07.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}糟糕的日子里　也爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}就算见不到面　也还惦记你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:18.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}到了下辈子　也还是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:23.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}Darlin', make me happy lalala I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:28.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}Darlin', make me happy lalala I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是何方神圣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你犯下的种种罪行 就以死偿还吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇拉大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么被原谅 也太轻巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八集 英雄猛进
